## Listing Accounts

> Example Request

```shell
curl <%=@api_prefix%>/2/account \
 -H "W-Token: <%=@wiw_token%>"
```
```php
<?php
$wiw = new Wheniwork("<%=@wiw_token%>");
$result = $wiw->get("account");
?>
```

